{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/articles/2018/02/15/1546344586289.html","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"e149695b-7485-5626-8a4b-54e24d286704","fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/02/15/1546344586289.html","birthTime":"2018-02-15T01:25:00.000Z","modifiedTime":"2019-01-01T12:44:00.054Z"},"html":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">Table of Contents</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_方法一\">方法一：</a></li>\n<li data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\"><a href=\"#_方法二\">方法二：</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preamble\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"quoteblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>在你的考试系统上配置接口 eth0 使用以下 IPV6地址： -\nserverx上的地址应该是 fddb:fe2a:ab1e::c0a8:1/64 -\n根据考试实际提供的地址配置 - desktopx上的地址应该是\nfddb:fe2a:ab1e::c0a8:2/64 - 两个系统必须能够与网络\nfddb:fe2a:able/64内的系统通信。 - 地址必须在重启后依旧生效。 -\n两个系统必须保持当前的 IPV4 地址并能通信</p>\n</div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h2 id=\"_方法一\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">方法一：</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>修改/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">DEVICE=eth0\nBOOTPROTO=static\nONBOOT=yes\nTYPE=Ethernet\nUSERCTL=yes\nPEERDNS=yes\nIPV6INIT=yes\nIPADDR=172.25.47.11\nPREFIX=24\nGATEWAY=172.25.47.254\nDNS1=172.254.254.254\nIPV6ADDR=\"fddb:fe2a:ab1e::c0a8:1/64\"\nIPV6_AUTOCONF=no</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">systemctl restart network</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/rhce/3.1.png\" alt=\"see\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<h2 id=\"_方法二\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">方法二：</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>通过nmcli控制</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">nmcli connection show              //查看当前的连接</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/6.png\" alt=\"see\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">nmcli connection modify \"System eth0\" ipv6.method manual ipv6.addresses \"fddb:fe2a:ab1e::c0a8:2/64\"\n\n# 重启查看\n\nsystemctl restart NetworkManager</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>配置完毕后nmcli con show查看</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/rhce/3.2.png\" alt=\"see\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>重启reboot</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<div class=\"content\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<img src=\"https://resources.echocow.cn/image/rhce/3.3.png\" alt=\"see\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" data-sal=\"fade\" data-sal-duration=\"500\" data-sal-repeat=\"true\">\n<p>只有一个</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"[rhce] 3 配置 IPV6 地址"},"pageAttributes":{"category":"rhce","description":"配置 IPV6 地址","image":"https://img.hacpai.com/bing/20180829.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1280/h/720/interlace/1/q/100","sort":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/articles/2018/02/15/1546344586289.html","next":{"document":{"title":"[rhce] 4 配置链路聚合"},"fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/02/16/1546344579957.html"}},"previous":{"document":{"title":"[rhce] 2 配置防火墙对 SSH 的限制"},"fields":{"slug":"/articles/2018/02/15/1546344574537.html"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3069561552","3673333084"]}